To access this forever on your mobile phone:
Since I am an AI code generator, I cannot host the site for you permanently. You need to deploy this code.

  1. Download the files or export this project.

  2. Upload them to a free static hosting provider like Vercel, Netlify, or GitHub Pages.

  3. Once deployed, they will give you a permanent URL (e.g., https://your-stitch-app.vercel.app).

  4. Open that link on your mobile phone, tap "Share" (iOS) or the Menu (Android), and select "Add to Home Screen". It will look and feel just like a native app.
